OL,3,CFloella Benjamin marks 30 years of
OL,4,CComing to England and why her story
OL,5,Cresonates
OL,7,FDame Floella Benjamin is celebrating
OL,8,Fthe 30th anniversary of her
OL,9,Fgroundbreaking children's book,
OL,10,F'Coming to England' which addresses
OL,11,Fthemes of the Windrush generation,
OL,12,Fimmigration, race, and integration.
OL,13,FITV News Arts Editor Nina Nannar
OL,14,Freports
OL,16,FWhen my parents came to the UK from
OL,17,FIndia, they faced frequent racism. But
OL,18,Fthey wanted us to absorb this foreign
OL,19,Fculture, to succeed and belong. To do
OL,20,Fthat, I needed role models.
