OL,4,CComing to England and why her story
OL,5,Cresonates
OL,7,FOn TV, they were scarce until
OL,8,FPlayschool popped up and into my
OL,9,Fconsciousness in the mid-70s. There
OL,10,Fwas this black lady, with beads in her
OL,11,Fhair, and every inch belonging in that
OL,12,FTV studio.
OL,14,FI can't tell you how massive the
OL,15,Fimpact was. She was lively, beautiful,
OL,16,Fand so confident in her skin.
