OL,3,CFloella Benjamin marks 30 years of
OL,4,CComing to England and why her story
OL,5,Cresonates
OL,7,FIt was only when her children's book
OL,8,F'Coming To England' was released in
OL,9,F1995 that I realised the highs and
OL,10,Flows Dame Floella Benjamin experienced
OL,11,Fas a child of the Windrush generation,
OL,12,Fleaving Trinidad in 1960 as a ten-year-
OL,13,Fold, and settling in an England that
OL,14,Foften made it clear she and her family
OL,15,Fwere not welcome.
OL,17,FIt spoke to me and millions of other
OL,18,Fimmigrants or children of immigrants.
