OL,3,CFloella Benjamin marks 30 years of
OL,4,CComing to England and why her story
OL,5,Cresonates
OL,7,FHer importance in the public life of
OL,8,Fthe UK cannot be overstated. She has
OL,9,Falways wanted to show what is
OL,10,Fpossible, even in the face of many
OL,11,Fobstacles.
OL,13,FAnd her simple, honest book lays her
OL,14,Fjourney out in a way children can
OL,15,Funderstand and she hopes, be inspired
OL,16,Fby.
